name: Coming Home
description: Coming home was never going to be easy.  There would be many difficulties to go beyond.  Many self limiting beliefs to slay and sometimes it felt like remaining asleep and staying in the comfort zone would be better.  Being here, now is more better than better and each part of the journey was and is totally worth it. Home has always been the present moment, where I AM...(Connect with me here https://twitter.com/CristinaSinned )
